    slug: 'poison-safety-children-home-guide',
    title: 'Poison Safety at Home: Protecting Children from Accidental Poisoning',
    category: 'Home Safety',
    excerpt: 'A comprehensive guide for parents on preventing accidental poisoning in children, covering medicines, household chemicals, plants, and what to do in a poisoning emergency.',
